snippet.title: Video Detective
snippet.description: The web's very first trailer site is now on YouTube! VideoDetective.com has over 250,000 movie trailers, TV previews, clips, international trailers, interviews, and video game trailers. We only distribute high quality official promotional videos. No bootlegs. No mashups. No broken links. Visit us at www.VideoDetective.com for detailed info including availability on every title, advanced search, tracking, and sharing options.
